Description (1,224 characters)

Commercialized Odakyu 8000 type 8258 formation with headlights replaced with white LEDs

-The front destination display is a lighting type, and the type destination display is a selection type from newly produced stickers. The vehicle number, OER mark, and brand mark are printed. Front and side type destination display (three-color LED), priority seat, car number display, weakly air-conditioned car, women-only car, Wheelchair/stroller mark can be selected from attached stickers (new production). User-installed train radio antenna, fuse box, front panel, and handrail. The signal flame tube and lightning arrestor are integrally sculpted. Headlights (white), taillights (red), front type and destination display (white) light up. The headlights of 8258 are lit in light bulb color. Equipped with coreless motor power unit with flywheel. Implemented long seat parts with car end. * The model railroad is a system that supplies power from the rails. Batteries are not used even when running, emitting light, or lighting. *Batteries are not included in this product. *This product does not use fuel. *Fuel is not included in this product. *Paint is not included in this product.
